{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-tsx","path":"/travel/2017/11/25/并不是特别值得一去的秦汉展.html","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"dca48761-6b50-5ea1-8c99-3486545ebc88","excerpt":"…","html":"<h1>并不是特别值得一去的秦汉展</h1>\n<p>今年大都会展了一个秦汉展,为了照顾国内情绪吧,国博也展了一个.\n即使是分段领票,但还是挤得一塌糊涂.</p>\n<p>因为距离发票还有一个半小时,我就先花时间重新逛了古代中国展.</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://ww1.sinaimg.cn/mw690/89d0a2e1ly1flvkd44in0j23vc2kw1l5.jpg\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://ww1.sinaimg.cn/mw690/89d0a2e1ly1flvkcz7q93j22kw3vc4qw.jpg\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://ww1.sinaimg.cn/mw690/89d0a2e1ly1flvkcygx92j23vc2kwu14.jpg\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://ww1.sinaimg.cn/mw690/89d0a2e1ly1flvkcxpaygj23vc2kw7wp.jpg\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://ww1.sinaimg.cn/mw690/89d0a2e1ly1flvkcauo4dj22kw3vc1l5.jpg\"></p>\n<p>展厅也不是很大,基本上算是大英的一半吧.\n里面的展品基本上也是石家庄\\陕西\\山西博物馆的,所以我基本上都见过了…</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://ww1.sinaimg.cn/mw690/89d0a2e1ly1flvkhetmk6j23vc2kwnpk.jpg\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://ww1.sinaimg.cn/mw690/89d0a2e1ly1flvkiah2o0j23vc2kwu13.jpg\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://ww1.sinaimg.cn/mw690/89d0a2e1ly1flvki8vhg9j23vc2kwu14.jpg\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://ww1.sinaimg.cn/large/89d0a2e1ly1flvkh2zrl9j23vc2kwhe0.jpg\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://ww1.sinaimg.cn/mw690/89d0a2e1ly1flvki8g3tdj23vc2kwu14.jpg\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://ww1.sinaimg.cn/large/89d0a2e1ly1flvkhofg03j23vc2kw1l5.jpg\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://ww1.sinaimg.cn/mw690/89d0a2e1ly1flvki7w3pbj23vc2kwkjs.jpg\"></p>\n<p>旁边的十月革命展览蛮有意思,虽然看不懂,但是好看呀.</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://ww1.sinaimg.cn/mw690/89d0a2e1ly1flvk75fn8qj23vc2kwx6w.jpg\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://ww1.sinaimg.cn/mw690/89d0a2e1ly1flvk70ny78j23vc2kwb2h.jpg\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://ww1.sinaimg.cn/mw690/89d0a2e1ly1flvk7b6vhjj23vc2kwhe1.jpg\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://ww1.sinaimg.cn/mw690/89d0a2e1ly1flvk7etysqj23vc2kwnpk.jpg\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://ww1.sinaimg.cn/mw690/89d0a2e1ly1flvjwxzltrj23vc2kwqvd.jpg\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://ww1.sinaimg.cn/mw690/89d0a2e1ly1flvk6uomu9j23vc2kwhe0.jpg\"></p>\n<p>临走前看了眼最喜欢的两尊菩萨像</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://ww1.sinaimg.cn/mw690/89d0a2e1ly1flvkk8i2ppj23vc2kw1l5.jpg\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://ww1.sinaimg.cn/mw690/89d0a2e1ly1flvkk19oytj23vc2kwkjs.jpg\"></p>","frontmatter":{"category":"travel"},"fields":{"slug":"/travel/2017/11/25/并不是特别值得一去的秦汉展.html","date":"November 25, 2017","title":"并不是特别值得一去的秦汉展"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/travel/2017/11/25/并不是特别值得一去的秦汉展.html","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/fe/2017/11/22/Building.Isomorphic.JavaScript.Apps.html","title":"Building.Isomorphic.JavaScript.Apps"},"frontmatter":{"category":"fe"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/tech/2017/11/26/给QA同学看的node科普.html","title":"给QA同学看的node科普"},"frontmatter":{"category":"tech"}}}}}